    <item>
      <title>My 2025 Checklist</title>
      <link>https://www.abdisalam.blog/blog/2025-checklist/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.abdisalam.blog/blog/2025-checklist/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This is the list I have laid out for myself, though I expect new ideas will arise as January unfolds. It serves as a rough outline, a gathering of thoughts and aspirations for the year ahead. My hope is that, by this time next year, these goals will stand fulfilled, each box checked with purpose.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Be conversational in Turkish&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Build some Swift apps&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Land new career opportunities&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Read 110 Books&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Bring new branches into The SISU Foundation&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Revise the Quran&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Get into cooking&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Bring out the prototype of Journa Media&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Master Web 2.0&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Travel to Liechtenstein&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox checked&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;X&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Try to get 3.7-4.0 GPA this year&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;box&#34;&gt;?&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div&gt;Do a Marathon run &lt;span class=&#34;quick-thought-indicator&#34; style=&#34;color: #ffb255 !important; cursor: pointer; margin-left: 5px;&#34; onclick=&#34;document.getElementById(&#39;marathon-thoughts&#39;).style.display = document.getElementById(&#39;marathon-thoughts&#39;).style.display === &#39;none&#39; ? &#39;block&#39; : &#39;none&#39;&#34;&gt;**&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div id=&#34;marathon-thoughts&#34; style=&#34;display: none; margin-left: 20px; padding-left: 10px; border-left: 2px solid #ffb255; font-size: 0.9em;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;p&gt;Planning to run the Istanbul Marathon in April 2025. Currently training and preparing for this goal.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
